      <title>减肥药制造商面临高盈利预期的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/obesity-drugmakers-face-the-test-of-high-earnings-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[礼来公司 (Eli Lilly &amp; Co.) 和诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 多年来的股价势头在最近几周停止了，这使得这两家减肥药物制造商本周的收益显得尤为重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/obesity-drugmakers-face-the-test-of-high-earnings-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
